description: The Carpool Karaoke trailer is here!
maintext:
The J Show
Apple Music is ready! The new 16 episode series of Carpool Karaoke is almost here and there will be surprises each week. Looks like James Corden is only in ONE episode with Will Smith, the rest will be pairing of your fav celebrities and it looks AMAZING.
title: [Watch] The New Carpool Karaoke Trailer Is Out And It Looks AMAZING
